                  </strong>
</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="42%" valign="TOP">
<p>1996 
              </p></td>
<td width="58%" valign="TOP">
<p align="RIGHT">1,250 
              </p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td width="42%" valign="TOP">
